title: The Jordan Westbrook 0 Gets A Slight Remix
content:
Home »Style » The Jordan Westbrook 0 Gets A Slight Remix	Posted on Sep 21, 2015Snakeskin is no stranger to the Jordan Brand, and it looks like one of their newer silhouettes is getting the luxe treatment. The Jordan Westbrook 0 is showing up more and more lately in some brand new colorways and we see this latest offering will be getting dressed in some new materials. This is the first signature shoe for Westbrook and instead of getting a model that could be worn on the court, the Jordan Brand chose to go a different route.
